    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designates usually slight and often temporary structures erected for the display or sale of merchandise or at which business is conducted.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
